high_descs: Turn right, go forward, then turn left to approach the bed.
Pick up the cell phone on the bed.
Turn around, move forward, then turn right to go towards the door, then turn right to face the desk.
Put the cell phone on the desk, in front of the computer.
anns.task_desc: Put the cell phone on the desk.

high_descs: Move to the right then straight facing the bed
Pick up the white phone on top of the bed
Carry the phone over to the desk facing the middle of the desk top
Place the phone on the middle front of the desk top
anns.task_desc: Move a phone to the desk

high_descs: Walk forward and slightly to the right towards the cell phone on the bed.
Pick up the cell phone from the bed.
Turn left and walk across the room to the desk on the right.
Put the cell phone on the desk, in front of the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Move a cell phone from a bed to a desk.
